metadata.description: ILLAZILLAZ ELEMENTZ is an NFT collection based on the designer wood toy originally created by TNES in 2007. ELEMENTZ is a collaborative project that merges the worlds of art, music, & fashion into a community where creatives can connect and network with like-minded ZILLAZ. Collector's who hold an ELEMENTZ NFT will get unique utility and exclusive VIP access to the expanding world of ILLAZILLAZ.
metadata.name: ILLAZILLAZ ELEMENTZ #1
